{"id":"entities/boeing","title":"Boeing","type":"entities","html":"<h1>Boeing</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Stub. American aerospace company on Yahir's March-22-2020 <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/covid-pandemic-era\">COVID crash</a> watchlist (<a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2020-03-22-stock-watchlist-march\">2020 03 22 stock watchlist march</a>) — flagged with the thesis <em>\"too important to lose\"</em> (i.e., government-backstop bet). Companion to <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/carnival-corp\">Carnival</a>, <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/beyond-meat\">Beyond Meat</a> in the same note.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2>Source summaries</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2020-03-22-stock-watchlist-march\">2020 03 22 stock watchlist march</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Connections</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/carnival-corp\">carnival corp</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/beyond-meat\">beyond meat</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/covid-pandemic-era\">covid pandemic era</a></li>\n</ul>\n","related":[{"id":"entities/beyond-meat","label":"Beyond Meat"},{"id":"entities/carnival-corp","label":"Carnival Corp"},{"id":"concepts/covid-pandemic-era","label":"COVID Pandemic Era"},{"id":"summaries/2020-03-22-stock-watchlist-march","label":"COVID-crash stock watchlist (March 22, 2020)"}]}
